FBIS4-41712 "drsov124_d_94011" FBIS-SOV-94-124 Daily Report 25 Jun 1994 Regional Affairs Commission Orders Debt Payment to Urals Arms Makers Commission Orders Debt Payment to Urals Arms Makers PM2706152594 Moscow KRASNAYA ZVEZDA in Russian 25 Jun 94 p 3 PM2706152594 Moscow KRASNAYA ZVEZDA Russian BFN ["Own Information" report from the "Fax News" roundup under "Russkoye Oruzhiye" rubric: "Decision to Repay Debts to South Urals Military-Industrial Complex"] [Text] Chelyabinsk -- "Defense sector workers in the southern Urals, where there is a concentration of unique enterprises producing missiles, nuclear weapons, electronic warfare equipment, and many more items essential to a modern army today, are in serious need of help," Viktor Glukhikh, chairman of the State Committee for the Defense Sectors of Industry, believes. A Russian Federation Government commission working in the Urals has instructed that debts to military-industrial complex enterprises in the oblast pertaining to work carried out under the state order be paid by 1 July this year.
